   <text>
      <body>
         <div type="translation">
            <ab>(Recto);;Apollonios to Zenon greeting. we have need of 400 fowls for fattening and of 100 hens. Kindly then buy them for us and send them to Ptolemais on the fork of the canal to our agent Dioskourides. Farewell. Year 35, Panemos 28, Epeiph 30.;;(Verso);;To Zenon.;(Docket, 2nd hand) Year 35, Mesore 7. Apollonios.</ab>
         </div>
